  "title": "Logistic Support Assistant",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Accurate system update and picking requirements</p></li><li><p>Good control of FIFO systems and other requirements for item picked</p></li><li><p>Proper handling of items picked</p></li><li><p>Maximize use of locations through good housekeeping control</p></li><li><p>Accurate preparation of customer’s packing requirements</p></li><li><p>Proper use of packing materials</p></li><li><p>Accurate application of labels and measurement for outbound shipments</p></li><li><p>Assist in cycle counts of items</p></li><li><p>Maintain general cleanliness of the outbound section</p></li><li><p>Maintain good care and usage of company’s equipment</p></li><li><p>Any other related projects/duties which not indicated above will be assigned by the superior from time to time</p></li></ul><p><strong>Education and Experience</strong></p><ul><li><p>Secondary qualification</p></li></ul><p><strong>Knowledge, Skills and Abilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Knowledge of electronic components product</p></li><li><p>Ability to recognize manufacturing data, eg. Data code, country of origin and etc</p></li><li><p>Computer knowledge and barcode technology</p></li><li><p>Operations of lifting equipment.</p></li><li><p>Effective communication skills</p></li></ul><p><br />\n\n</p>",
